> Subject: Re: [T2] Re: head bolts

> Only once? A lot of folks like to put the heads on, put on 
> the head nuts, then torque in stages. Take it to 10 lb-ft, 
> let it sit for 20 minutes or so, go to 15 lb-ft, let sit for 
> 20 minutes, go to final torque, let sit for 20 minutes, then 
> check the torque on the head nuts one final time and leave 
> it. This gives the engine time to accept the fact that it's 
> going to have heads on it whether it likes them or not.
> -- 
